summary:
AN (ALMOST) IMPOSSIBLE CHALLENGE

 Solve all the riddles around a wooden box, pull or push levers and buttons, rotate wheels, and, most of all, use your brain. 

The box contains a remote to open the metal shutter and help you gain your freedom.
